- put these lines in your ../vim5x/filetype.vim file together with the other "au" 
lines:

" Ferite Scripting language
au BufNewFile,BufRead *.fe                      set ft=ferite_script
au BufNewFile,BufRead *.fec                     set ft=ferite_module


- put these lines in you ../vim5x/syntax/synload..vim file together with the other 
"SynAu" lines:
SynAu ferite_script
SynAu ferite_module


copy ferite_script.vim and ferite_module.vim to your ../vim5x/syntax directory
